859
00:34:04,357 --> 00:34:05,917
That's called self-deception.

860
00:34:06,837 --> 00:34:07,998
I got it right?

861
00:34:09,277 --> 00:34:09,958
Yes,

862
00:34:10,878 --> 00:34:12,358
I'm improving.

863
00:34:19,157 --> 00:34:20,637
Min Hui.

