898
00:35:32,797 --> 00:35:33,558
Min Hui,

899
00:35:33,558 --> 00:35:35,398
I know raising me is tiring for you.

900
00:35:35,518 --> 00:35:37,237
But soon,

901
00:35:37,438 --> 00:35:39,637
